<h1>Particulars of Claim</h1>
<p><strong>{{brand_name}}</strong></p>

<hr>

<p><strong>Claimant:</strong> {{claimant_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Defendant:</strong> {{defendant_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Claim type:</strong> {{claim_label}}</p>

<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>{{claim_summary}}</p>

{{#if category_context}}
<h2>Background facts</h2>
<p>{{category_context}}</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Legal basis</h2>
<p>{{legal_rules.legal_basis}}</p>

<h2>Required elements checked by the interview</h2>
<ol>
  {{#each required_element_checks}}
  <li>{{element}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ol>

{{#if category_facts.length}}
<h2>Category-specific facts</h2>
<table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  {{#each category_facts}}
  <tr>
    <td width="35%"><strong>{{label}}</strong></td>
    <td width="65%">{{value}}</td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
</table>
{{/if}}

<h2>Pre-action conduct</h2>
<p>{{pre_action_summary}}</p>
{{#if pre_action_sent_date}}
<p>The most recent clear demand was sent on {{pre_action_sent_date}}.</p>
{{/if}}
{{#if response_deadline}}
<p>The defendant was asked to respond by {{response_deadline}}.</p>
{{/if}}
<p><em>{{legal_rules.pre_action_rule}}</em></p>

<h2>Amount claimed</h2>
<p>
  The claimant claims {{currency total_claim_amount}}, as particularised in the attached Schedule of Loss,
  plus the court fee and any interest the court allows.
</p>

{{#if claim_interest}}
<h2>Interest</h2>
<p>
  The claimant has asked for interest to be considered. The pack records a review rate of
  {{interest_rate}}% per year{{#if interest_start_date}} from {{interest_start_date}}{{/if}} and a daily figure of {{currency daily_interest}}. The claimant should check
  the legal basis before filing.
</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Relief sought</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Judgment for {{currency total_claim_amount}}.</li>
  <li>The issue fee of {{currency court_fee}}.</li>
  {{#if claim_interest}}
  <li>Interest if the court is satisfied it is recoverable.</li>
  {{/if}}
  <li>Any further order the court considers appropriate.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Statement of truth</h2>
<p>I believe that the facts stated in these particulars of claim are true.</p>
<p>Signed: _________________________ {{signatory_name}}</p>
<p>Dated: _________________________ {{signature_date}}</p>
<p><em>This document must be checked, signed, and dated before filing.</em></p>
